sentences.sentence: Easy removal of MCB, RCD or main incomer from an assembled unit, offering simple fitting of additional or replacement components without removal of the busbar.
sentences.translation: 微型断路器、漏电断路器及主开关可于组件上轻易拆除，提供简便的更换装配而不需拆除母线。

sentences.sentence: With taxes and prices also lower, an incomer from California might easily save 30% or more of his salary by moving from Silicon Valley to the "Silicon Hills" of Austin.
sentences.translation: 如此低税收和房价，如果从加州硅谷搬至奥斯丁的“硅山”，一个人可以很容易就省下30%以上的工资。
